This paper deals with the capacity region of a relay network, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The use of detour schemes and routing also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the sub-categories of signal processing (cs.SI) and computer communication (cs.CC). Finally, the mention of multicast capacity in the title suggests that the paper may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
